All Implemented Interfaces:
org.opensearch.core.common.io.stream.Writeable
public class NodePrometheusMetricsResponse extends org.opensearch.core.action.ActionResponse
Action response class for Prometheus Exporter plugin. This class a container of other responses that are needed to construct list of all required metrics. It knows how to prepare all data for wire transport by writing it into outputStream.
